cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with control of piecewise affine systems, which are commonly used in robotics and control systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization and computational techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses a sampling-based approach, which is a common technique in machine learning and data science, indicating that it could also be categorized as cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
